"author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 29, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"\"Give glad tidings to those who walk to the mosque in darkness,\"","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/category\/hadith-chapters\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21491,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/fitnah-al-masiha-al-dajjal\/","url_meta":{"origin":14749,"position":3},"title":"Tribulation of the False Messiah, al-Masiha al-Dajjal","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\"Know that your Lord does not have one eye.\"","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0625\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0625\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21235,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/ten-ayat-surah-kahf-dajjal\/","url_meta":{"origin":14749,"position":4},"title":"Ten verses of Surat al-Kahf to protect from Dajjal","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 20, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\"Whoever contemplates them will not be misled by the trials of the False Messiah.\"","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Noble Quran \u0627\u0644\u0642\u0631\u0622\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0643\u0631\u064a\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Noble Quran \u0627\u0644\u0642\u0631\u0622\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0643\u0631\u064a\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/category\/noble-quran\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12837,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/an-nawawi-on-good-character-manners\/","url_meta":{"origin":14749,"position":5},"title":"Imam al-Nawawi on Good